    "description":  "Help and guidance for limited company directors.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003eHelp us to improve the director information hub by \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.smartsurvey.co.uk/s/PCI2DV/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ecompleting a short feedback survey.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"overview\"\u003eOverview\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs a company director, you will need support and guidance throughout the lifespan of your company.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe government offers help and guidance for company directors on GOV.UK.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThere are also many private sector organisations and professional bodies that offer help and services. This is offered both paid-for and free of charge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt is important when you deal with organisations and bodies like these, you understand what you are paying for from the beginning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"company-advisory-and-membership-services\"\u003eCompany advisory and membership services\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/company-health-check-keeping-your-business-on-track#your-new-responsibilities\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eCompany health check: keeping your business on track\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGuidance from the Insolvency Service.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/business-support-helpline\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eBusiness advice and support\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGovernment help and advice for UK businesses.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.thedirectorshelpline.org/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eThe Directors Helpline\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFree, impartial guidance for businesses.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.fsb.org.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eThe Federation of Small Businesses\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eMember organisation for small business owners.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eBusiness and self-employed on GOV.UK\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTools and guidance for businesses.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.iod.com\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eInstitute of Directors\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eMembership organisation for company directors.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.businessdebtline.org\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eBusiness Debtline\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDebt advice service from The Money Advice Trust.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"local-support-for-businesses\"\u003eLocal support for businesses\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub-regional-support-for-companies-in-england\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eEngland\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub-support-for-companies-in-wales\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eWales\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub-support-for-companies-in-scotland\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eScotland\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub-support-for-companies-in-northern-ireland\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eNorthern Ireland\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"financing-information\"\u003eFinancing information\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.british-business-bank.co.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eBritish Business Bank\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGovernment-owned business development bank.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.ukfinance.org.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eUK Finance\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOrganisation that represents the banking and finance industry, offering advice to that sector.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"company-turnaround-and-business-recovery\"\u003eCompany turnaround and business recovery\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.the-ift.com/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eThe Institute for Turnaround\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFind company turnaround and business recovery advice as well as a list of experts in the field.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.r3.org.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eR3\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFind UK insolvency and restructuring practitioners as well as advice from this membership organisation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"government-resources-for-limited-company-directors\"\u003eGovernment resources for limited company directors\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/being-a-company-director\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eBeing a company director \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eCompanies House guidance on being a director.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/help-and-support-for-company-directors\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eHMRC updates\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eUpdates, webinars and information for directors from HMRC.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"resources-for-financial-difficulty\"\u003eResources for financial difficulty\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/protecting-company-from-compulsory-liquidation\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eDealing with company debt\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInformation on GOV.UK\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/applying-for-a-moratorium-under-the-corporate-insolvency-and-governance-act-2020\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eCompany moratorium\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInformation from the Insolvency Service.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.smallbusinesscommissioner.gov.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eSmall Business Commissioner\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHelp with customer payment problems.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/options-when-a-company-is-insolvent\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eOptions when a company is insolvent\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInformation on GOV.UK\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/options-if-youre-owed-money\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eOptions if you’re owed money\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInformation on GOV.UK\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"find-accountancy-and-tax-services\"\u003eFind accountancy and tax services\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.icaew.com\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eICAEW\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eChartered accountants in England, Wales and Northern Ireland.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.icas.com\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eICAS\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eChartered accountants in Scotland.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.accaglobal.com/uk/en/member/find-an-accountant.html?isocountry=GB\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eACCA\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGlobal organisation for professional accountants.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.cipfa.org/members/members-directory\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eCIPFA\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eChartered Institute of public finance and accountancy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/how-to-choose-a-tax-agent\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eHow to choose a tax agent\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHMRC information on choosing a tax agent.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/director-information-hub\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGo back to the director information hub homepage.\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
